{"tid":2070417,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警申匿名被駁回 官憂令傳媒不積極報導 未能引公眾關注","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T07:59:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8738fc70d8c1023c9d7b98f8ab17e0fc64856212","tid":2070417,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:21:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074688&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CzHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=19aba330\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074688&h=39c18d07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074688</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）20歲聽障學生被控於9月15日「港島自由行」期間，在銅鑼灣港鐵站外襲警。案件今日（6月19日）在東區裁判法院提堂，控方在上次提堂時為控方證人高級警司申請匿名，今被駁回。裁判官認為，控方為警員申請匿名的證據空泛，高等法院去年頒布的禁制令，亦已有效地減少警員被「起底」個案。同時，裁判官擔心警員匿名可能令傳媒不積極報導，未能適切地引起公眾關注。案件押後至7月17日，期間被告獲准以原有條件保釋。"},{"pid":"fdba3a37cff2ad567a94a7ca1d6fc6e8703758ea","tid":2070417,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"黃官 本土派！"},{"pid":"aa4dfbb34a01568a89e6fd1584e01a2d40e79dc4","tid":2070417,"uid":37869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"法官：你都on99 我批准咪到我比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f386b73e467d10d8e19b0667a1f3cf5cede51924","tid":2070417,"uid":216939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:30:31.000Z","msg":"其實已經有禁制令唔比起底，係都要申請匿名哂時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceacd43495c475057eaab60f30e16ba10eb05db","tid":2070417,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa4dfbb34a01568a89e6fd1584e01a2d40e79dc4","tid":2070417,"uid":37869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"法官：你都on99 我批准咪到我比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma